# Vite Vue Starter

This is a project template using [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/). It requires [Node.js](https://nodejs.org) version 18+ or 20+.

To start:

```sh
npm install
npm run dev

# if using yarn:
yarn
yarn dev

# if using pnpm:
pnpm install
pnpm run dev
```
